<LP>
   FUJI BANK Ltd. (Tokyo) -- Steven A. Schwimmer was named
managing director of the new derivative products group,
responsible for interest-rate and currency swaps and options,
at Fuji Capital Markets Corp., a New York-based subsidiary of
this bank. Mr. Schwimmer, 36 years old, was previously a
director in the interest-rate swaps department at CS First
Boston, a New York-based investment bank.
</LP>
