<HL>
   Business Brief -- La Quinta Motor Inns Inc.:
   Brierley's Industrial Equity
   Increases Holding to 14.4%
</HL>
<DATE>
08/08/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   LQM A.IEL A.BRY
</CO>
<IN>
TENDER OFFERS, MERGERS, ACQUISITIONS (TNM)
</IN>
<LP>
   Industrial Equity (Pacific) Ltd., a Hong Kong investment
firm, said it raised its stake in La Quinta Motor Inns Inc.,
San Antonio, Texas, to 14.4% of the common shares
outstanding.
   In a Securities and Exchange Commission filing, Industrial
Equity, a publicly traded company controlled by Brierley
Investments Ltd. of New Zealand, said it holds 1,883,600 La
